      "side": 1,
      "message": "Done. Recursion is possible here: resolving can unify other nodes, whose schedulers run their own resolver tasks, so a nested processResolver could clobber the flag — in particular clearing it after our own lookup had set it, silently dropping the conjunct again. Made it stack-based by saving and restoring the flag around r.resolve, and noted this in the field\u0027s doc comment.",
